caption: Had a great chat with my friend @jermainedvauz 🫶🏼 The best piece of advice I ever got was to ‘always be yourself - but know that you’re never gonna be everyone’s cup of tea’. And it’s so true…not everyone is gonna like you…and that’s ok! Be yourself, it’s the key to happiness. Lean into the people that love you and don’t try and change yourself to please everyone because you’ll never be able to! Do you boo 👌🏼
